text: Mary Moody is an Australian author. Mary Moody may also refer to: * Mary Blair Moody (1837 – 1919), American physician * Mary Moody Northen (1892 – 1986), née Mary Moody, American financier and philanthropist ==See also== * Mary Moody Emerson (1774 – 1863), American letter writer and diarist
title: Mary Moody (disambiguation)
